%N A394449 Number of symmetric relations on an n-set that are neither reflexive nor transitive.
%F A394449 a(n) = A006125(n+1) - A006125(n) - A000110(n+1) + A000110(n).
%e A394449 On a 2-set {1,2}, there are exactly 3 such relations. Such relations on {1,2} are {(1,2),(2,1)}, {(1,1),(1,2),(2,1)}, {(2,2),(1,2),(2,1)}. So, a(2)=3.
%Y A394449 Cf. A006125, A000110, A005493, A202534, A394620, A006905, A000798, A053763.
